premise_source_doc_sentence: The play was performed at the Swan Theatre in Stratford-upon-Avon and the National Arts Centre in Ottawa during the summer and fall of 2007 by an all-female cast led by director Josette Bushell-Mingo .
This is the first season since Season 3 to have more female cast members then male and the last season to do so .
This season is also notable for being the last season to feature more female cast members than male , until season 9 .
Denberg was the last original female cast member on the show before her departure .
In January 2012 , the show opened in Toronto at Nightwood Theatre , with an all-female cast led by director Kelly Thornton and starring Megan Follows as Penelope .
